Precondition: cases for verify in Chrome browser

TC_1

Summary:
Checking operation of "registration form" with correct values

Steps:
1) Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2) Enter correct values in "Email" text field (Student)
3) Enter correct values in "Password" text field (909090)
4) Click on "Submit" button

Expected result:
Authorization must be successful. "Home" page should be open.

TC_2

Summary:
Checking operation of "registration form" with incorrect values

Steps:
1) Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2) Enter incorrect values in "Email" text field (ex qwerty)
3) Enter incorrect values in "Password" text field (ex asdfg)
4) Click on "Submit" button


Expected result:
Authorization must fail. "Home" page should be open.

TC_3

Summary:
Check the ability to add  new device in dictionary

Steps:
1) Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2) Enter correct values in "Email" text field (Student)
3) Enter correct values in "Password" text field (909090)
4) Click on "Submit" button
5) In "side menu" click on "dictionary" dropdown
6) In "dictionary" dropdown click on "Device"  item
7) Click on "Add" button
8) Enter correct values in "Apparat nubmer" text field (ex 000111 )
9) Enter correct values in "Apparat comment" text field (ex TV remote. Nice device for lazy people)
10) Click on "Create" button

Actual result:
Must be created a new device with number "000111" and comment "TV remote. Nice device for lazy people"


TC_4

Summary:
Check the ability to add  new service

Steps:
1) Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2) Enter correct values in "Email" text field (Student)
3) Enter correct values in "Password" text field (909090)
4) Click on "Submit" button
5) In "side menu" click on "service" dropdown
6) Click on "Add" button
7) Enter correct values in "Service changes" text field (ex test changes_1 )
8) Enter correct values in "Service operations" text field (ex test_operations_1)
9) Enter correct values in "Service date" date picker (ex 20.dec.2017 20:00)
10) Enter correct values in "staff" text field (ex TV remote. Nice device for lazy people)
11) Enter correct values in "associate" text field (ex Vinigradov Alexey Petrovi4)
12) Click on "Create" button

Actual result:
Must be created a new service



